br>
 &nbsp;</span></p>
<ul>
<li class=3D"t-rtf-style--body3"><span style=3D"color: rgb(92,122,140);">Us=
e at least 16 characters with a mix of letters, numbers, and symbols.</span=
></li>
<li class=3D"t-rtf-style--body3"><span style=3D"color: rgb(92,122,140);">Ne=
ver reuse passwords across multiple online accounts to keep yourself safer =
if a security breach strikes.</span></li>
<li class=3D"t-rtf-style--body3"><span style=3D"color: rgb(92,122,140);">Av=
oid saving passwords in your web browsers to reduce the chances of curious =
hands or even hackers from accessing them.</span></li>
<li class=3D"t-rtf-style--body3"><span style=3D"color: rgb(92,122,140);">Us=
e a password generator, like our <strong>Random password generator</strong>=
 at Avast for a simple way to create more effective passwords.</span></li>
<li class=3D"t-rtf-style--body3"><span style=3D"color: rgb(92,122,140);">St=
ore passwords safely in a secure password manager, not in an unsecured onli=
ne location or in plain text.</span></li>
